OL,6,FCCTV shows Daniel Cleveland stealing
OL,7,Ftaps and throwing items over the fence
OL,8,Fof a garden centre.
OL,10,FA prolific shoplifter who targeted
OL,11,Ftaps at DIY stores across the south of
OL,12,FEngland has been jailed.
OL,14,FMetropolitan Police said an estimated
OL,15,F#16,000 worth of items, mainly taps,
OL,16,Fwere stolen from B&Q stores in Kent,
OL,17,FHampshire, Buckinghamshire, Essex and
OL,18,FGreenwich over a 13-month period.
