OL,4,Cthousands of pounds worth of taps
OL,6,FDaniel Cleveland, 33, of Bromley,
OL,7,Fpleaded guilty to nine counts of theft
OL,8,Fand three counts of attempted theft at
OL,9,FLewes Crown Court and has been
OL,10,Fsentenced to three years in jail.
OL,12,FChief Inspector Rav Pathania, the
OL,13,FMet's lead for tackling retail crime,
OL,14,Fsaid: "The Met is prioritising
OL,15,Fneighbourhood policing, putting more
OL,16,Fofficers in local teams to tackle
OL,17,Fissues that matter most to Londoners,
OL,18,Fincluding shoplifting.
