OL,6,F"Officers worked with B&Q to review
OL,7,Fnine reports of theft and three
OL,8,Freports of attempted theft carried out
OL,9,Fbetween February 2024 and March 2025.
OL,11,F"We work with businesses to target the
OL,12,Fmost prolific offenders, as we know
OL,13,Fthe fear they cause retail workers and
OL,14,Fthe negative impact their offending
OL,15,Fhas on communities.
OL,17,F"As a result, neighbourhood crime is
OL,18,Fdown 15.5 per cent this year and we
OL,19,Fhave solved 92 per cent more
OL,20,Fshoplifting so far this year."
