OL,6,FPolice said Cleveland worked with
OL,7,Fanother man to steal the goods.
OL,9,FIn one instance, at B&Q Larkfield in
OL,10,FKent, security cameras caught
OL,11,FCleveland and his accomplice throwing
OL,12,Fthe stolen items over a fence from
OL,13,Finside the garden centre of the store.
OL,15,FThe men then collected the goods from
OL,16,Fthe other side and bundled them into a
OL,17,Fgetaway vehicle with false plates.
OL,19,FBodycam footage shows Cleveland being
OL,20,Farrested at his home on Wednesday 30
OL,21,FApril.
