OL,6,FSimon Moss, B&Q Security and
OL,7,FCommercial Stockloss Manager, said:
OL,8,F"This case highlights the power of
OL,9,Fcollaboration and intelligence sharing
OL,10,Fbetween retailers and the police.
OL,12,F"It sends a clear message to those who
OL,13,Ftarget B&Q and other retailers that we
OL,14,Fwill take every appropriate action to
OL,15,Fidentify offenders and fully support
OL,16,Flaw enforcement in bringing them to
OL,17,Fjustice.
