OL,6,F"Shoplifting is not a victimless
OL,7,Fcrime. B&Q is firmly committed to
OL,8,Fprotecting and supporting our
OL,9,Fcolleagues from the impacts of
OL,10,Fshoplifting, and to the safety and
OL,11,Fsecurity of our customers."
OL,13,FEnquiries are ongoing to locate the
OL,14,Fother man. The location of the stolen
OL,15,Fgoods remains unknown.
OL,17,FThe thefts and attempted thefts took
OL,18,Fplace at the following stores:
